\s UWIRATA YIRATE KRISTO
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Uwirata yirate Kristo, uwirata yirate \bd*\bd Ubuntu; \bd*\bd ni co cirato nyakuri, kukw’\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd inyama n’amaraso, bitazoragwa Ubwami bw’Imana.\bd*
\pc \bdit Uko nik’Uhoraho agize ng’\bdit*\bdit  \bdit*\bdit umunyabwenge yoye, kwirata \bdit*\bdit ubwenge \bdit*\bdit bwiwe; umunyenkomezi yoye, kwirat’\bdit*\bdit  \bdit*\bdit inkomezi ziwe; cank’\bdit*\bdit  \bdit*\bdit umutunzi yoye, kwirat’\bdit*\bdit  \bdit*\bdit ubutunzi bwiwe;\bdit*\bdit  \bdit*\bdit ./.Arik’\bdit*\bdit  \bdit*\bdit uwirata yirate ko yamenye, Uhoraho n’ubushobozi bwiwe./.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Uhoraho niwe umutima wawe ukwiriye kwirata; abaciye bugufi bazovyumva, banezerezwe n’ico, ico nico Uhoraho \bd*\bd Ashaka\bd*\bd .\bd*
\pc \bdit Uko nik’Uhoraho agize ng’\bdit*\bdit  \bdit*\bdit umunyabwenge yoye, kwirata ubwenge bwiwe; umunyenkomezi yoye, kwirat’ inkomezi ziwe; cank’ umutunzi yoye, kwirat’ ubutunzi bwiwe; ./.Arik’ uwirata yirate ko yamenye, Uhoraho n’ubushobozi bwiwe./.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Niwe yakweretse iciza ic’ari co, akwerek’ivy’\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd umuhezagiro; akwereka ivy’umuvumo, niwe vyirato vyawe hose ugendane nawe wicishije bugufi.\bd*
\pc \bdit Uko nik’Uhoraho agize ng’umunyabwenge yoye, kwirata ubwenge bwiwe; umunyenkomezi yoye, kwirat’ inkomezi ziwe; cank’ umutunzi yoye, kwirat’ ubutunzi bwiwe; ./.Arik’ uwirata yirate ko yamenye, Uhoraho n’ubushobozi bwiwe./.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Niw’aduha kuba muri Kristo, yaduhindukiy’\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd ubwenge nyakuri; yaduhindukiy’\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd ukugororoka kugira ngo tubone gucungurwa ng’uwirata yirate Kristo.\bd*
\pc \bdit Uko nik’Uhoraho agize ng’\bdit*\bdit  \bdit*\bdit umunyabwenge yoye, kwirata ubwenge bwiwe; umunyenkomezi yoye, kwirat’ inkomezi ziwe; cank’ umutunzi yoye, kwirat’ ubutunzi bwiwe; ./.Arik’ uwirata yirate ko yamenye, Uhoraho n’ubushobozi bwiwe./.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Uwirata yirate Uhoraho, kuk’\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd umuntu yishimagiza, atari we yemerwa namba, ariko hemerwa uw’\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd Umwami, ni we vyirato vyawe hose.\bd*
